#
# 01. POST /ngsi-ld/v1/subscriptions, with sub-id http://a.b.c/subs/sub01
# 02. Check mongo
# 03. GET /ngsi-ld/v1/subscription/http://a.b.c/subs/sub01, see @context in HTTP header
